2. **Application:** `src/Server/Core.Application/Features/{{{ input }}}/Commands/Create{{{ input }}}Command.cs` (MediatR Handler + FluentValidator).
3. **Infrastructure:** `src/Server/Infrastructure/Persistence/Configurations/{{{ input }}}Configuration.cs` (Fluent API Mapping).
4. **Client:** `src/Client/features/{{{ input }}}/{{{ input }}}.component.ts` (Standalone, OnPush, Signals).

Ensure C# 14 file-scoped namespaces and Angular 21 Signal patterns are used.